title: Independent candidate Fazal Haq wins PK-31 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Fazal Haq won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK-31, Upper Kohistan by securing 14,384 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was an Independent candidate satbar Khan who bagged 9,185 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turnout remained 50.43 per cent.
